{"article_id":"xlRfN1RSuc9BJc7G","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The White House acknowledged for the first time Monday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that President Obama ' s oft-repeated promise","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that everyone can keep their health insurance plans under Obamacare","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"just isn ' t true .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"For more than three years","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"as he worked for enactment of the Affordable Care Act","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and encouraged people to enroll ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Obama routinely pledged","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that people could keep their doctors and their plans","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"if they liked them .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"\" If you like your health care plan ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"you will be able to keep your health care plan .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Period , \"","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Obama said in June 2009 .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Later that year , he proclaimed ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"\" Nothing in our plan requires you to change what you have . \"","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"With thousands of people across the country receiving cancellation notices from their insurers ,","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"the White House acknowledged Monday","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that some consumers will be required to switch plans ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"which could mean switching doctors .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"White House press secretary Jay Carney said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"it ' s because the health care law requires certain standards of coverage .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"\" It ' s true there are existing health care plans on the individual market","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that do not meet those minimum standards","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and therefore do not qualify for the Affordable Care Act , \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Mr. Carney said .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Former presidential adviser David Axelrod said Monday on MSNBC","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that most people","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"who have insurance","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"can keep their plans ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and those","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"who lose their plans","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"will be \" transferred to higher-quality plans with subsidies . \"","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"But many middle-class families are finding out","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that they will be required to pay higher premiums for new plans","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and that they don ' t qualify for subsidies .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Dianne Barrette , 56 , of Florida , recently learned","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that her health care plan was not comprehensive enough","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"to meet coverage requirements","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"set by the Affordable Care Act .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"She was informed that her plan will cost 10 times more than her current premium of $ 50 per month .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"\" What I have right now is what I ' m happy with , \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"she told CBS News .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"\" I just want to know","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"why I can ' t keep what I have . \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell , Kentucky Republican , said","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"it ' s more proof","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Obamacare isn ' t working .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"\" For months , the American people have been learning about the impact","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Obamacare will have on individuals and families in the form of higher premiums , canceled insurance plans , and lost jobs","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"- more broken promises from the administration , \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. McConnell said .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"\" Obamacare costs too much","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"and it ' s not working the way","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"they promised .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Obamacare ' s problems run much deeper than the failed website ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"and it ' s time","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"for the president to keep his word . \"","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"The latest Obamacare controversy erupted","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"as Mr. Obama prepares to fly to Boston on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"to give a speech","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"promoting the benefits of the program .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"The White House timed the president ' s event for the same day","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"that Health and Human Services Secretary Kathleen Sebelius is expected to receive a grilling from congressional Republicans at a hearing on the early failures of the healthcare.gov website .","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"White House aides said","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"more than 80 percent of Americans won ' t be required to change health insurers ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"either because they get coverage through their employers","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"or they are covered by Medicare or Medicaid .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Asked by a reporter about a family in North Carolina","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that discovered","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"their premiums will rise 430 percent ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Mr. Carney said","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"he could not address individual complaints .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"But he said","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"\" bare-bones \" insurance policies were \" part of the problem . \"","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" It is not a fair comparison","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"to compare those kinds of plans ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"which were part of the problem ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to the basic level insurance","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that ' s provided under the Affordable Care Act , \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Carney said.","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Valerie Jarrett went to Twitter on Monday night","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"to take a different tack ,","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"blaming the insurance companies .","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"\" FACT :","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"Nothing in # Obamacare forces people out of their health plans .","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"No change is required","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"unless insurance companies change existing plans , \"","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"the White House senior adviser wrote .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":177,"left":146,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":104,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":92,"right":103,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":0,"right":91,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":90,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":90,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":97,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":95,"right":96,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":94,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":4,"right":93,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":113,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":107,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"p